{"work":"KJV + Strong's","code":"Tit","book":"Titus","chapterCount":3,"chapters":[{"number":1,"verses":[{"id":"Tit|1|1","reference":"Titus 1:1","number":1,"text":"Paul, a servant of God, and an apostle of Jesus Christ, according to the faith of God's elect, and the acknowledging of the truth which is after godliness;","strongs":[{"label":"Paul","strongsId":"G3972"},{"label":"a servant","strongsId":"G1401"},{"label":"of God","strongsId":"G2316"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G1161"},{"label":"an apostle","strongsId":"G652"},{"label":"of Jesus","strongsId":"G2424"},{"label":"Christ","strongsId":"G5547"},{"label":"according to","strongsId":"G2596"},{"label":"the faith","strongsId":"G4102"},{"label":"of God's","strongsId":"G2316"},{"label":"elect","strongsId":"G1588"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"the acknowledging","strongsId":"G1922"},{"label":"of the truth","strongsId":"G225"},{"label":"which","strongsId":"G3588"},{"label":"is after","strongsId":"G2596"}]},{"id":"Tit|1|2","reference":"Titus 1:2","number":2,"text":"In hope of eternal life, which God, that cannot lie, promised before the world began;","strongs":[{"label":"In","strongsId":"G1909"},{"label":"hope","strongsId":"G1680"},{"label":"of eternal","strongsId":"G166"},{"label":"life","strongsId":"G2222"},{"label":"which","strongsId":"G3739"},{"label":"God","strongsId":"G2316"},{"label":"that cannot lie","strongsId":"G893"},{"label":"promised","strongsId":"G1861"},{"label":"before","strongsId":"G4253"},{"label":"the world","strongsId":"G166"}]},{"id":"Tit|1|3","reference":"Titus 1:3","number":3,"text":"But hath in due times manifested his word through preaching, which is committed unto me according to the commandment of God our Saviour;","strongs":[{"label":"But","strongsId":"G1161"},{"label":"hath","strongsId":"G5319"},{"label":"in due","strongsId":"G2398"},{"label":"times","strongsId":"G2540"},{"label":"manifested","strongsId":"G5319"},{"label":"his","strongsId":"G846"},{"label":"word","strongsId":"G3056"},{"label":"through","strongsId":"G1722"},{"label":"preaching","strongsId":"G2782"},{"label":"which","strongsId":"G3739"},{"label":"is committed","strongsId":"G4100"},{"label":"unto me","strongsId":"G1473"},{"label":"according to","strongsId":"G2596"},{"label":"the commandment","strongsId":"G2003"},{"label":"of God","strongsId":"G2316"},{"label":"our","strongsId":"G2257"}]},{"id":"Tit|1|4","reference":"Titus 1:4","number":4,"text":"To Titus, <em>mine</em> own son after the common faith: Grace, mercy, <em>and</em> peace, from God the Father and the Lord Jesus Christ our Saviour.","strongs":[{"label":"To Titus","strongsId":"G5103"},{"label":"em>mine</em> own","strongsId":"G1103"},{"label":"son","strongsId":"G5043"},{"label":"after","strongsId":"G2596"},{"label":"the common","strongsId":"G2839"},{"label":"faith","strongsId":"G4102"},{"label":"Grace","strongsId":"G5485"},{"label":"mercy","strongsId":"G1656"},{"label":"em>and</em> peace","strongsId":"G1515"},{"label":"from","strongsId":"G575"},{"label":"God","strongsId":"G2316"},{"label":"the Father","strongsId":"G3962"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"the Lord","strongsId":"G2962"},{"label":"Jesus","strongsId":"G2424"},{"label":"Christ","strongsId":"G5547"},{"label":"our","strongsId":"G2257"}]},{"id":"Tit|1|5","reference":"Titus 1:5","number":5,"text":"For this cause left I thee in Crete, that thou shouldest set in order the things that are wanting, and ordain elders in every city, as I had appointed thee:","strongs":[{"label":"For this","strongsId":"G5127"},{"label":"cause","strongsId":"G5484"},{"label":"left I","strongsId":"G2641"},{"label":"thee","strongsId":"G4571"},{"label":"in","strongsId":"G1722"},{"label":"Crete","strongsId":"G2914"},{"label":"that","strongsId":"G2443"},{"label":"thou shouldest set in order","strongsId":"G1930"},{"label":"the things that are wanting","strongsId":"G3007"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"ordain","strongsId":"G2525"},{"label":"elders","strongsId":"G4245"},{"label":"in every","strongsId":"G2596"},{"label":"city","strongsId":"G4172"},{"label":"as","strongsId":"G5613"},{"label":"I","strongsId":"G1473"},{"label":"had appointed","strongsId":"G1299"}]},{"id":"Tit|1|6","reference":"Titus 1:6","number":6,"text":"If any be blameless, the husband of one wife, having faithful children not accused of riot or unruly.","strongs":[{"label":"If any","strongsId":"G1536"},{"label":"be","strongsId":"G2076"},{"label":"blameless","strongsId":"G410"},{"label":"the husband","strongsId":"G435"},{"label":"of one","strongsId":"G3391"},{"label":"wife","strongsId":"G1135"},{"label":"having","strongsId":"G2192"},{"label":"faithful","strongsId":"G4103"},{"label":"children","strongsId":"G5043"},{"label":"not","strongsId":"G3361"},{"label":"accused","strongsId":"G1722"},{"label":"accused","strongsId":"G2724"},{"label":"of riot","strongsId":"G810"},{"label":"or","strongsId":"G2228"}]},{"id":"Tit|1|7","reference":"Titus 1:7","number":7,"text":"For a bishop must be blameless, as the steward of God; not selfwilled, not soon angry, not given to wine, no striker, not given to filthy lucre;","strongs":[{"label":"For","strongsId":"G1063"},{"label":"a bishop","strongsId":"G1985"},{"label":"must","strongsId":"G1163"},{"label":"be","strongsId":"G1511"},{"label":"blameless","strongsId":"G410"},{"label":"as","strongsId":"G5613"},{"label":"the steward","strongsId":"G3623"},{"label":"of God","strongsId":"G2316"},{"label":"not","strongsId":"G3361"},{"label":"selfwilled","strongsId":"G829"},{"label":"not","strongsId":"G3361"},{"label":"soon angry","strongsId":"G3711"},{"label":"not","strongsId":"G3361"},{"label":"given to wine","strongsId":"G3943"},{"label":"no","strongsId":"G3361"},{"label":"striker","strongsId":"G4131"},{"label":"not","strongsId":"G3361"}]},{"id":"Tit|1|8","reference":"Titus 1:8","number":8,"text":"But a lover of hospitality, a lover of good men, sober, just, holy, temperate;","strongs":[{"label":"But","strongsId":"G235"},{"label":"a lover of hospitality","strongsId":"G5382"},{"label":"a lover of good men","strongsId":"G5358"},{"label":"sober","strongsId":"G4998"},{"label":"just","strongsId":"G1342"},{"label":"holy","strongsId":"G3741"}]},{"id":"Tit|1|9","reference":"Titus 1:9","number":9,"text":"Holding fast the faithful word as he hath been taught, that he may be able by sound doctrine both to exhort and to convince the gainsayers.","strongs":[{"label":"Holding fast","strongsId":"G472"},{"label":"the faithful","strongsId":"G4103"},{"label":"word","strongsId":"G3056"},{"label":"as","strongsId":"G2596"},{"label":"he hath been taught","strongsId":"G1322"},{"label":"that","strongsId":"G2443"},{"label":"he may be","strongsId":"G5600"},{"label":"able","strongsId":"G1415"},{"label":"by","strongsId":"G1722"},{"label":"sound","strongsId":"G5198"},{"label":"doctrine","strongsId":"G1319"},{"label":"both","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"to exhort","strongsId":"G3870"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"to convince","strongsId":"G1651"}]},{"id":"Tit|1|10","reference":"Titus 1:10","number":10,"text":"For there are many unruly and vain talkers and deceivers, specially they of the circumcision:","strongs":[{"label":"For","strongsId":"G1063"},{"label":"there are","strongsId":"G1526"},{"label":"many","strongsId":"G4183"},{"label":"unruly","strongsId":"G506"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"vain talkers","strongsId":"G3151"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"deceivers","strongsId":"G5423"},{"label":"specially","strongsId":"G3122"},{"label":"they of","strongsId":"G1537"}]},{"id":"Tit|1|11","reference":"Titus 1:11","number":11,"text":"Whose mouths must be stopped, who subvert whole houses, teaching things which they ought not, for filthy lucre's sake.","strongs":[{"label":"Whose","strongsId":"G3739"},{"label":"mouths","strongsId":"G1993"},{"label":"must","strongsId":"G1163"},{"label":"be stopped","strongsId":"G1993"},{"label":"who","strongsId":"G3748"},{"label":"subvert","strongsId":"G396"},{"label":"whole","strongsId":"G3650"},{"label":"houses","strongsId":"G3624"},{"label":"teaching","strongsId":"G1321"},{"label":"things which","strongsId":"G3739"},{"label":"they ought","strongsId":"G1163"},{"label":"not","strongsId":"G3361"},{"label":"for","strongsId":"G5484"},{"label":"filthy","strongsId":"G150"},{"label":"lucre's","strongsId":"G2771"}]},{"id":"Tit|1|12","reference":"Titus 1:12","number":12,"text":"One of themselves, <em>even</em> a prophet of their own, said, The Cretians <em>are</em> alway liars, evil beasts, slow bellies.","strongs":[{"label":"One","strongsId":"G5100"},{"label":"of","strongsId":"G1537"},{"label":"themselves","strongsId":"G846"},{"label":"em>even</em> a prophet","strongsId":"G4396"},{"label":"of their","strongsId":"G846"},{"label":"own","strongsId":"G2398"},{"label":"said","strongsId":"G2036"},{"label":"The Cretians","strongsId":"G2912"},{"label":"em>are</em> alway","strongsId":"G104"},{"label":"liars","strongsId":"G5583"},{"label":"evil","strongsId":"G2556"},{"label":"beasts","strongsId":"G2342"},{"label":"slow","strongsId":"G692"}]},{"id":"Tit|1|13","reference":"Titus 1:13","number":13,"text":"This witness is true. Wherefore rebuke them sharply, that they may be sound in the faith;","strongs":[{"label":"This","strongsId":"G3778"},{"label":"witness","strongsId":"G3141"},{"label":"is","strongsId":"G2076"},{"label":"true","strongsId":"G227"},{"label":"Wherefore","strongsId":"G1223"},{"label":"Wherefore","strongsId":"G3739"},{"label":"Wherefore","strongsId":"G156"},{"label":"rebuke","strongsId":"G1651"},{"label":"them","strongsId":"G846"},{"label":"sharply","strongsId":"G664"},{"label":"that","strongsId":"G2443"},{"label":"they may be sound","strongsId":"G5198"},{"label":"in","strongsId":"G1722"}]},{"id":"Tit|1|14","reference":"Titus 1:14","number":14,"text":"Not giving heed to Jewish fables, and commandments of men, that turn from the truth.","strongs":[{"label":"Not","strongsId":"G3361"},{"label":"giving heed","strongsId":"G4337"},{"label":"to Jewish","strongsId":"G2451"},{"label":"fables","strongsId":"G3454"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"commandments","strongsId":"G1785"},{"label":"of men","strongsId":"G444"},{"label":"that turn from","strongsId":"G654"}]},{"id":"Tit|1|15","reference":"Titus 1:15","number":15,"text":"Unto the pure all things <em>are</em> pure: but unto them that are defiled and unbelieving <em>is</em> nothing pure; but even their mind and conscience is defiled.","strongs":[{"label":"Unto the pure","strongsId":"G2513"},{"label":"all things","strongsId":"G3956"},{"label":"em>are</em> pure","strongsId":"G3303"},{"label":"em>are</em> pure","strongsId":"G2513"},{"label":"but","strongsId":"G1161"},{"label":"unto them that are defiled","strongsId":"G3392"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"unbelieving","strongsId":"G571"},{"label":"em>is</em> nothing","strongsId":"G3762"},{"label":"pure","strongsId":"G2513"},{"label":"but","strongsId":"G235"},{"label":"even","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"their","strongsId":"G846"},{"label":"mind","strongsId":"G3563"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"conscience","strongsId":"G4893"}]},{"id":"Tit|1|16","reference":"Titus 1:16","number":16,"text":"They profess that they know God; but in works they deny <em>him</em>, being abominable, and disobedient, and unto every good work reprobate.","strongs":[{"label":"They profess","strongsId":"G3670"},{"label":"that they know","strongsId":"G1492"},{"label":"God","strongsId":"G2316"},{"label":"but","strongsId":"G1161"},{"label":"in works","strongsId":"G2041"},{"label":"they deny","strongsId":"G720"},{"label":"em>him</em>, being","strongsId":"G5607"},{"label":"abominable","strongsId":"G947"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"disobedient","strongsId":"G545"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"unto","strongsId":"G4314"},{"label":"every","strongsId":"G3956"},{"label":"good","strongsId":"G18"},{"label":"work","strongsId":"G2041"}]}]},{"number":2,"verses":[{"id":"Tit|2|1","reference":"Titus 2:1","number":1,"text":"But speak thou the things which become sound doctrine:","strongs":[{"label":"But","strongsId":"G1161"},{"label":"speak","strongsId":"G2980"},{"label":"thou","strongsId":"G4771"},{"label":"the things which","strongsId":"G3739"},{"label":"become","strongsId":"G4241"},{"label":"sound","strongsId":"G5198"}]},{"id":"Tit|2|2","reference":"Titus 2:2","number":2,"text":"That the aged men be sober, grave, temperate, sound in faith, in charity, in patience.","strongs":[{"label":"That the aged men","strongsId":"G4246"},{"label":"be","strongsId":"G1511"},{"label":"sober","strongsId":"G3524"},{"label":"grave","strongsId":"G4586"},{"label":"temperate","strongsId":"G4998"},{"label":"sound","strongsId":"G5198"},{"label":"in faith","strongsId":"G4102"},{"label":"in charity","strongsId":"G26"}]},{"id":"Tit|2|3","reference":"Titus 2:3","number":3,"text":"The aged women likewise, that <em>they be</em> in behaviour as becometh holiness, not false accusers, not given to much wine, teachers of good things;","strongs":[{"label":"The aged women","strongsId":"G4247"},{"label":"likewise","strongsId":"G5615"},{"label":"that <em>they be</em> in","strongsId":"G1722"},{"label":"behaviour","strongsId":"G2688"},{"label":"as becometh holiness","strongsId":"G2412"},{"label":"not","strongsId":"G3361"},{"label":"false accusers","strongsId":"G1228"},{"label":"not","strongsId":"G3361"},{"label":"given","strongsId":"G1402"},{"label":"to much","strongsId":"G4183"},{"label":"wine","strongsId":"G3631"}]},{"id":"Tit|2|4","reference":"Titus 2:4","number":4,"text":"That they may teach the young women to be sober, to love their husbands, to love their children,","strongs":[{"label":"That","strongsId":"G2443"},{"label":"they may teach","strongsId":"G4994"},{"label":"the young women","strongsId":"G3501"},{"label":"to be","strongsId":"G1511"},{"label":"sober","strongsId":"G4994"},{"label":"to love their husbands","strongsId":"G5362"}]},{"id":"Tit|2|5","reference":"Titus 2:5","number":5,"text":"<em>To be</em> discreet, chaste, keepers at home, good, obedient to their own husbands, that the word of God be not blasphemed.","strongs":[{"label":"em>To be</em> discreet","strongsId":"G4998"},{"label":"chaste","strongsId":"G53"},{"label":"keepers at home","strongsId":"G3626"},{"label":"good","strongsId":"G18"},{"label":"obedient","strongsId":"G5293"},{"label":"to their own","strongsId":"G2398"},{"label":"husbands","strongsId":"G435"},{"label":"that","strongsId":"G3363"},{"label":"the word","strongsId":"G3056"},{"label":"of God","strongsId":"G2316"},{"label":"be","strongsId":"G987"},{"label":"not","strongsId":"G3363"}]},{"id":"Tit|2|6","reference":"Titus 2:6","number":6,"text":"Young men likewise exhort to be sober minded.","strongs":[{"label":"Young men","strongsId":"G3501"},{"label":"likewise","strongsId":"G5615"},{"label":"exhort","strongsId":"G3870"}]},{"id":"Tit|2|7","reference":"Titus 2:7","number":7,"text":"In all things shewing thyself a pattern of good works: in doctrine <em>shewing</em> uncorruptness, gravity, sincerity,","strongs":[{"label":"In","strongsId":"G4012"},{"label":"all things","strongsId":"G3956"},{"label":"shewing","strongsId":"G3930"},{"label":"thyself","strongsId":"G4572"},{"label":"a pattern","strongsId":"G5179"},{"label":"of good","strongsId":"G2570"},{"label":"works","strongsId":"G2041"},{"label":"in","strongsId":"G1722"},{"label":"doctrine","strongsId":"G1319"},{"label":"em>shewing</em> uncorruptness","strongsId":"G90"},{"label":"gravity","strongsId":"G4587"}]},{"id":"Tit|2|8","reference":"Titus 2:8","number":8,"text":"Sound speech, that cannot be condemned; that he that is of the contrary part may be ashamed, having no evil thing to say of you.","strongs":[{"label":"Sound","strongsId":"G5199"},{"label":"speech","strongsId":"G3056"},{"label":"that cannot be condemned","strongsId":"G176"},{"label":"that","strongsId":"G2443"},{"label":"he that is of","strongsId":"G1537"},{"label":"the contrary part","strongsId":"G1727"},{"label":"may be ashamed","strongsId":"G1788"},{"label":"having","strongsId":"G2192"},{"label":"no","strongsId":"G3367"},{"label":"evil","strongsId":"G5337"},{"label":"thing","strongsId":"G3367"},{"label":"to say","strongsId":"G3004"},{"label":"of","strongsId":"G4012"}]},{"id":"Tit|2|9","reference":"Titus 2:9","number":9,"text":"<em>Exhort</em> servants to be obedient unto their own masters, <em>and</em> to please <em>them</em> well in all <em>things</em>; not answering again;","strongs":[{"label":"em>Exhort</em> servants","strongsId":"G1401"},{"label":"to be obedient","strongsId":"G5293"},{"label":"unto their own","strongsId":"G2398"},{"label":"masters","strongsId":"G1203"},{"label":"em>and</em> to","strongsId":"G1511"},{"label":"please <em>them</em> well","strongsId":"G2101"},{"label":"in","strongsId":"G1722"},{"label":"all","strongsId":"G3956"},{"label":"em>things</em>; not","strongsId":"G3361"}]},{"id":"Tit|2|10","reference":"Titus 2:10","number":10,"text":"Not purloining, but shewing all good fidelity; that they may adorn the doctrine of God our Saviour in all things.","strongs":[{"label":"Not","strongsId":"G3361"},{"label":"purloining","strongsId":"G3557"},{"label":"but","strongsId":"G235"},{"label":"shewing","strongsId":"G1731"},{"label":"all","strongsId":"G3956"},{"label":"good","strongsId":"G18"},{"label":"fidelity","strongsId":"G4102"},{"label":"that","strongsId":"G2443"},{"label":"they may adorn","strongsId":"G2885"},{"label":"the doctrine","strongsId":"G1319"},{"label":"of God","strongsId":"G2316"},{"label":"our","strongsId":"G2257"},{"label":"Saviour","strongsId":"G4990"},{"label":"in","strongsId":"G1722"}]},{"id":"Tit|2|11","reference":"Titus 2:11","number":11,"text":"For the grace of God that bringeth salvation hath appeared to all men,","strongs":[{"label":"For","strongsId":"G1063"},{"label":"the grace","strongsId":"G5485"},{"label":"of God","strongsId":"G2316"},{"label":"that bringeth salvation","strongsId":"G4992"},{"label":"hath appeared","strongsId":"G2014"},{"label":"to all","strongsId":"G3956"}]},{"id":"Tit|2|12","reference":"Titus 2:12","number":12,"text":"Teaching us that, denying ungodliness and worldly lusts, we should live soberly, righteously, and godly, in this present world;","strongs":[{"label":"Teaching","strongsId":"G3811"},{"label":"us","strongsId":"G2248"},{"label":"that","strongsId":"G2443"},{"label":"denying","strongsId":"G720"},{"label":"ungodliness","strongsId":"G763"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"worldly","strongsId":"G2886"},{"label":"lusts","strongsId":"G1939"},{"label":"we should live","strongsId":"G2198"},{"label":"soberly","strongsId":"G4996"},{"label":"soberly","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"righteously","strongsId":"G1346"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"godly","strongsId":"G2153"},{"label":"in","strongsId":"G1722"},{"label":"this present","strongsId":"G3568"}]},{"id":"Tit|2|13","reference":"Titus 2:13","number":13,"text":"Looking for that blessed hope, and the glorious appearing of the great God and our Saviour Jesus Christ;","strongs":[{"label":"Looking for","strongsId":"G4327"},{"label":"that blessed","strongsId":"G3107"},{"label":"hope","strongsId":"G1680"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"the glorious","strongsId":"G1391"},{"label":"appearing","strongsId":"G2015"},{"label":"of the great","strongsId":"G3173"},{"label":"God","strongsId":"G2316"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"our","strongsId":"G2257"},{"label":"Saviour","strongsId":"G4990"},{"label":"Jesus","strongsId":"G2424"}]},{"id":"Tit|2|14","reference":"Titus 2:14","number":14,"text":"Who gave himself for us, that he might redeem us from all iniquity, and purify unto himself a peculiar people, zealous of good works.","strongs":[{"label":"Who","strongsId":"G3739"},{"label":"gave","strongsId":"G1325"},{"label":"himself","strongsId":"G1438"},{"label":"for","strongsId":"G5228"},{"label":"us","strongsId":"G2257"},{"label":"that","strongsId":"G2443"},{"label":"he might redeem","strongsId":"G3084"},{"label":"us","strongsId":"G2248"},{"label":"from","strongsId":"G575"},{"label":"all","strongsId":"G3956"},{"label":"iniquity","strongsId":"G458"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"purify","strongsId":"G2511"},{"label":"unto himself","strongsId":"G1438"},{"label":"a peculiar","strongsId":"G4041"},{"label":"people","strongsId":"G2992"},{"label":"zealous","strongsId":"G2207"},{"label":"of good","strongsId":"G2570"}]},{"id":"Tit|2|15","reference":"Titus 2:15","number":15,"text":"These things speak, and exhort, and rebuke with all authority. Let no man despise thee.","strongs":[{"label":"These things","strongsId":"G5023"},{"label":"speak","strongsId":"G2980"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"exhort","strongsId":"G3870"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"rebuke","strongsId":"G1651"},{"label":"with","strongsId":"G3326"},{"label":"all","strongsId":"G3956"},{"label":"authority","strongsId":"G2003"},{"label":"Let","strongsId":"G4065"},{"label":"no man","strongsId":"G3367"},{"label":"despise","strongsId":"G4065"}]}]},{"number":3,"verses":[{"id":"Tit|3|1","reference":"Titus 3:1","number":1,"text":"Put them in mind to be subject to principalities and powers, to obey magistrates, to be ready to every good work,","strongs":[{"label":"Put","strongsId":"G5279"},{"label":"them","strongsId":"G846"},{"label":"in mind","strongsId":"G5279"},{"label":"to be subject","strongsId":"G5293"},{"label":"to principalities","strongsId":"G746"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"powers","strongsId":"G1849"},{"label":"to obey magistrates","strongsId":"G3980"},{"label":"to be","strongsId":"G1511"},{"label":"ready","strongsId":"G2092"},{"label":"to","strongsId":"G4314"},{"label":"every","strongsId":"G3956"},{"label":"good","strongsId":"G18"}]},{"id":"Tit|3|2","reference":"Titus 3:2","number":2,"text":"To speak evil of no man, to be no brawlers, <em>but</em> gentle, shewing all meekness unto all men.","strongs":[{"label":"To speak evil of","strongsId":"G987"},{"label":"no man","strongsId":"G3367"},{"label":"to be","strongsId":"G1511"},{"label":"no brawlers","strongsId":"G269"},{"label":"em>but</em> gentle","strongsId":"G1933"},{"label":"shewing","strongsId":"G1731"},{"label":"all","strongsId":"G3956"},{"label":"meekness","strongsId":"G4236"},{"label":"unto","strongsId":"G4314"},{"label":"all","strongsId":"G3956"}]},{"id":"Tit|3|3","reference":"Titus 3:3","number":3,"text":"For we ourselves also were sometimes foolish, disobedient, deceived, serving divers lusts and pleasures, living in malice and envy, hateful, <em>and</em> hating one another.","strongs":[{"label":"For","strongsId":"G1063"},{"label":"we ourselves","strongsId":"G2249"},{"label":"also","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"were","strongsId":"G2258"},{"label":"sometimes","strongsId":"G4218"},{"label":"foolish","strongsId":"G453"},{"label":"disobedient","strongsId":"G545"},{"label":"deceived","strongsId":"G4105"},{"label":"serving","strongsId":"G1398"},{"label":"divers","strongsId":"G4164"},{"label":"lusts","strongsId":"G1939"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"pleasures","strongsId":"G2237"},{"label":"living","strongsId":"G1236"},{"label":"in","strongsId":"G1722"},{"label":"malice","strongsId":"G2549"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"envy","strongsId":"G5355"},{"label":"hateful","strongsId":"G4767"},{"label":"em>and</em> hating","strongsId":"G3404"}]},{"id":"Tit|3|4","reference":"Titus 3:4","number":4,"text":"But after that the kindness and love of God our Saviour toward man appeared,","strongs":[{"label":"But","strongsId":"G1161"},{"label":"after","strongsId":"G3753"},{"label":"that the kindness","strongsId":"G5544"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"love","strongsId":"G5363"},{"label":"of God","strongsId":"G2316"},{"label":"our","strongsId":"G2257"},{"label":"Saviour","strongsId":"G4990"},{"label":"toward man","strongsId":"G5363"}]},{"id":"Tit|3|5","reference":"Titus 3:5","number":5,"text":"Not by works of righteousness which we have done, but according to his mercy he saved us, by the washing of regeneration, and renewing of the Holy Ghost;","strongs":[{"label":"Not","strongsId":"G3756"},{"label":"by","strongsId":"G1537"},{"label":"works","strongsId":"G2041"},{"label":"of","strongsId":"G1722"},{"label":"righteousness","strongsId":"G1343"},{"label":"which","strongsId":"G3739"},{"label":"we","strongsId":"G2249"},{"label":"have done","strongsId":"G4160"},{"label":"but","strongsId":"G235"},{"label":"according to","strongsId":"G2596"},{"label":"his","strongsId":"G846"},{"label":"mercy","strongsId":"G1656"},{"label":"he saved","strongsId":"G4982"},{"label":"us","strongsId":"G2248"},{"label":"by","strongsId":"G1223"},{"label":"the washing","strongsId":"G3067"},{"label":"of regeneration","strongsId":"G3824"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"renewing","strongsId":"G342"},{"label":"of the Holy","strongsId":"G40"}]},{"id":"Tit|3|6","reference":"Titus 3:6","number":6,"text":"Which he shed on us abundantly through Jesus Christ our Saviour;","strongs":[{"label":"Which","strongsId":"G3739"},{"label":"he shed","strongsId":"G1632"},{"label":"on","strongsId":"G1909"},{"label":"us","strongsId":"G2248"},{"label":"abundantly","strongsId":"G4146"},{"label":"through","strongsId":"G1223"},{"label":"Jesus","strongsId":"G2424"},{"label":"Christ","strongsId":"G5547"},{"label":"our","strongsId":"G2257"}]},{"id":"Tit|3|7","reference":"Titus 3:7","number":7,"text":"That being justified by his grace, we should be made heirs according to the hope of eternal life.","strongs":[{"label":"That","strongsId":"G2443"},{"label":"being justified by","strongsId":"G1344"},{"label":"his","strongsId":"G1565"},{"label":"grace","strongsId":"G5485"},{"label":"we should be made","strongsId":"G1096"},{"label":"heirs","strongsId":"G2818"},{"label":"according to","strongsId":"G2596"},{"label":"the hope","strongsId":"G1680"},{"label":"of eternal","strongsId":"G166"}]},{"id":"Tit|3|8","reference":"Titus 3:8","number":8,"text":"<em>This is</em> a faithful saying, and these things I will that thou affirm constantly, that they which have believed in God might be careful to maintain good works. These things are good and profitable unto men.","strongs":[{"label":"em>This is</em> a faithful","strongsId":"G4103"},{"label":"saying","strongsId":"G3056"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"these things","strongsId":"G4012"},{"label":"these things","strongsId":"G5130"},{"label":"I will","strongsId":"G1014"},{"label":"that thou","strongsId":"G4571"},{"label":"affirm constantly","strongsId":"G1226"},{"label":"that","strongsId":"G2443"},{"label":"they which have believed","strongsId":"G4100"},{"label":"in God","strongsId":"G2316"},{"label":"might be careful","strongsId":"G5431"},{"label":"to maintain","strongsId":"G4291"},{"label":"good","strongsId":"G2570"},{"label":"works","strongsId":"G2041"},{"label":"These things","strongsId":"G5023"},{"label":"are","strongsId":"G2076"},{"label":"good","strongsId":"G2570"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"profitable","strongsId":"G5624"}]},{"id":"Tit|3|9","reference":"Titus 3:9","number":9,"text":"But avoid foolish questions, and genealogies, and contentions, and strivings about the law; for they are unprofitable and vain.","strongs":[{"label":"But","strongsId":"G1161"},{"label":"avoid","strongsId":"G4026"},{"label":"foolish","strongsId":"G3474"},{"label":"questions","strongsId":"G2214"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"genealogies","strongsId":"G1076"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"contentions","strongsId":"G2054"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"strivings about","strongsId":"G3163"},{"label":"the law","strongsId":"G3544"},{"label":"for","strongsId":"G1063"},{"label":"they are","strongsId":"G1526"},{"label":"unprofitable","strongsId":"G512"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"}]},{"id":"Tit|3|10","reference":"Titus 3:10","number":10,"text":"A man that is an heretick after the first and second admonition reject;","strongs":[{"label":"A man","strongsId":"G444"},{"label":"that is an heretick","strongsId":"G141"},{"label":"after","strongsId":"G3326"},{"label":"the first","strongsId":"G3391"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"second","strongsId":"G1208"},{"label":"admonition","strongsId":"G3559"}]},{"id":"Tit|3|11","reference":"Titus 3:11","number":11,"text":"Knowing that he that is such is subverted, and sinneth, being condemned of himself.","strongs":[{"label":"Knowing","strongsId":"G1492"},{"label":"that","strongsId":"G3754"},{"label":"he that is such","strongsId":"G5108"},{"label":"is subverted","strongsId":"G1612"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"sinneth","strongsId":"G264"},{"label":"being","strongsId":"G5607"}]},{"id":"Tit|3|12","reference":"Titus 3:12","number":12,"text":"When I shall send Artemas unto thee, or Tychicus, be diligent to come unto me to Nicopolis: for I have determined there to winter.","strongs":[{"label":"When","strongsId":"G3752"},{"label":"I shall send","strongsId":"G3992"},{"label":"Artemas","strongsId":"G734"},{"label":"unto","strongsId":"G4314"},{"label":"thee","strongsId":"G4571"},{"label":"or","strongsId":"G2228"},{"label":"Tychicus","strongsId":"G5190"},{"label":"be diligent","strongsId":"G4704"},{"label":"to come","strongsId":"G2064"},{"label":"unto","strongsId":"G4314"},{"label":"me","strongsId":"G3165"},{"label":"to","strongsId":"G1519"},{"label":"Nicopolis","strongsId":"G3533"},{"label":"for","strongsId":"G1063"},{"label":"I have determined","strongsId":"G2919"},{"label":"there","strongsId":"G1563"}]},{"id":"Tit|3|13","reference":"Titus 3:13","number":13,"text":"Bring Zenas the lawyer and Apollos on their journey diligently, that nothing be wanting unto them.","strongs":[{"label":"Bring","strongsId":"G4311"},{"label":"Zenas","strongsId":"G2211"},{"label":"the lawyer","strongsId":"G3544"},{"label":"and","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"Apollos","strongsId":"G625"},{"label":"on their journey","strongsId":"G4311"},{"label":"diligently","strongsId":"G4709"},{"label":"that","strongsId":"G2443"},{"label":"nothing","strongsId":"G3367"},{"label":"be wanting","strongsId":"G3007"}]},{"id":"Tit|3|14","reference":"Titus 3:14","number":14,"text":"And let ours also learn to maintain good works for necessary uses, that they be not unfruitful.","strongs":[{"label":"And","strongsId":"G1161"},{"label":"let","strongsId":"G3129"},{"label":"ours","strongsId":"G2251"},{"label":"also","strongsId":"G2532"},{"label":"learn","strongsId":"G3129"},{"label":"to maintain","strongsId":"G4291"},{"label":"good","strongsId":"G2570"},{"label":"works","strongsId":"G2041"},{"label":"for","strongsId":"G1519"},{"label":"necessary","strongsId":"G316"},{"label":"uses","strongsId":"G5532"},{"label":"that","strongsId":"G3363"},{"label":"they be","strongsId":"G5600"},{"label":"not","strongsId":"G3363"}]},{"id":"Tit|3|15","reference":"Titus 3:15","number":15,"text":"All that are with me salute thee. Greet them that love us in the faith. Grace <em>be</em> with you all. Amen.","strongs":[{"label":"All","strongsId":"G3956"},{"label":"that are with","strongsId":"G3326"},{"label":"me","strongsId":"G1700"},{"label":"salute","strongsId":"G782"},{"label":"thee","strongsId":"G4571"},{"label":"Greet","strongsId":"G782"},{"label":"them that love","strongsId":"G5368"},{"label":"us","strongsId":"G2248"},{"label":"in","strongsId":"G1722"},{"label":"the faith","strongsId":"G4102"},{"label":"Grace","strongsId":"G5485"},{"label":"em>be</em> with","strongsId":"G3326"},{"label":"you","strongsId":"G5216"},{"label":"all","strongsId":"G3956"}]}]}]}
